company_name: GRANJA EL PILAR DE ALDEA SOCIEDAD AGRARIA DE TRANSFORMACION NUM. 4148
information: The company GRANJA EL PILAR DE ALDEA SOCIEDAD AGRARIA DE TRANSFORMACION NUM. 4148, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1949, which operates in the Poultry, rabbits and game - farming industry. It is based in L Aldea, Spain.
